metadata.name: Kiki #1
metadata.description: Kiki City is a collection of 1111 unique Kikis that are living on the ETH blockchain! Every Kiki is guaranteed to be distinctive from the others. Enjoy spending your time as a Kiki City citizen by participating in weekly and monthly Kiki events like video-game tournaments, art challenges, movie days, and more! The Kiki mission is to create a fun, wholesome community space of passionate creatives that love spending time with other NFT hobbyists and enthusiasts.
